			<p>An attorney for 27 years, Mike is a <%= link_to('trial lawyer', 'http://www.thenationaltriallawyers.org/', :target => '_blank') %> and has tried hundreds of cases to verdict. He specializes in <%= link_to('municipal', '/practice-areas/local-government-and-municipal-law', :target => '_blank') %> and <%= link_to('criminal law', '/practice-areas/criminal-law', :target => '_blank') %> and has zealously represented hundreds of individuals in criminal proceedings, both felonies and misdemeanors, throughout the state of Michigan. In addition, he has served as municipal prosecutor and an assistant city attorney for the cities of <%= link_to('Trenton,', 'http://www.trentonmi.org/index-home.asp', :target => '-blank') %> <%= link_to('Belleville', 'http://www.belleville.mi.us/cob/bhome.htm', :target => '_blank') %> and <%= link_to('Melvindale,', 'http://www.melvindale.org/', :target => '_blank') %> and currently represents <%= link_to('the city of Riverview', 'http://www.cityofriverview.com/', :target => '_blank') %> and <%= link_to('the Charter Township of Royal Oak', 'http://www.royaloaktwp.com/', :target => '_blank') %> in those capacities. He also served as indigent defense counsel for 10 years in the <%= link_to('19th (Dearborn) District Court,', 'http://www.cityofdearborn.org/government/19th-district-court', :target => '_blank') %> where he gained invaluable trial experience.</p>

			<p>Mike also manages an active general practice of law with an emphasis on litigation. He has represented individuals, small business owners and large corporations alike in litigation throughout the state on issues ranging from secured transactions, contracts, <%= link_to('real estate,', '/practice-areas/real-estate-transactions-and-litigation', :target =>'_blank') %> debt collections and <%= link_to('landlord tenant matters.', '/practice-areas/landlord-and-tenant-law', :target => '_blank') %></p>

			<p>Mike’s courtroom experience has spanned from appearing in district, circuit and probate courts throughout the state, the <%= link_to('state court of appeals,', 'http://courts.mi.gov/courts/coa/pages/default.aspx', :target => '_blank') %> <%= link_to('federal court,', 'http://www.gsa.gov/portal/content/105041', :target =>'_blank') %> bankruptcy court and a wide variety of administrative law cases, including workers compensation, <%= link_to('secretary of state', 'http://www.michigan.gov/sos', :target => '_blank') %> hearings, unemployment hearings, LCC and business licensing hearings.</p>

